CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 26, 1955, pg. A1 reads: "Honor Mrs. Gandy - Mrs. J.M. Gandy, left, with Mrs. Harry A. Wheatley Jr. and T.C. Wallace, president of the local chapter of the Virginia State College Alumni Association. Mrs. Gandy is the widow of the late president of the school. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Mrs. J.M. Gandy, T.C. Wallace, and Mrs. Harry A. Wheatley Jr. posed behind table in Greene Hearth
